Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,5,,久违的陆地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚踏实地的感觉真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然热血的我还是最适合这广袤的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的热血也只能持续到下个港口为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否改走陆路前往雷之国呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计没戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在身处水之国的境内
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由大大小小的岛屿组成的水之国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同雷之国并未接壤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…一想到要乘船就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那离雷之国还有多远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概还有四分之一的路程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 在港口听闻附近有山寨出没
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:00:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无怨无仇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此相遇就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下买路财吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个护额是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是来自木叶以身弑晓的漩涡鸣人大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 山寨就是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一模一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里像了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们无视我 还在吐槽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是木叶的漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我算个啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连自己是谁都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥你们也带着木叶的护额呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是真正的漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹牛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,货真价实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过没想到竟然山寨鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来名气十足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能摆平他的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的…决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此一决胜负 看看谁才是真正的鸣人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 努力战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输了的话他就是真货咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴倒是嚣张得很
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这连热身运动都算不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西我们没收了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么处置这个男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在赶路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种家伙 暴打一顿扔路边就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他逃掉再制造麻烦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可就声名狼藉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我负责追踪这名盗贼 名叫伊己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢和这家伙对峙的屈指可数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看也就我俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙可是让人闻风丧胆的大盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙才不是漩涡鸣人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了…我才是正品漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你是真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 我的大名竟然被盗贼所用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太混蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你在追踪这盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是官府人士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后就拜托这位大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶紧上路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大哥…你没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来可没有那么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人不可貌相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是忍者大师伊已大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来您这么牛逼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不能以貌取人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是被干掉了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想干掉他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你也听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是真正的漩涡鸣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到会在这里遇到真货
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳 你的借口我不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来计划好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我干掉身为盗贼的你 从而提升我的名望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在即将打响的战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有名望可无法展现自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果干掉漩涡鸣人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能大名远扬了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…这么危险的事打住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你的恩惠你都忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在一个人孤独地哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己是我唯一的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过下次要找我们能干掉的做对手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫我们能干掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我动真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管它是一个还是两个漩涡鸣人 都不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我吧 伊己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了就好 能明白的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人在这附近当山贼是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经有数人遇险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是个大红脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为何鸣人会在这里做山贼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙不是拯救了村子的英雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细情况还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有传言说漩涡鸣人在村里是个麻烦的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许成为叛忍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果叛离村子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶应当也在追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住他再转卖给木叶 一定能有个好价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没问题吗 对方可是漩涡鸣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说漩涡鸣人连中忍考试都没通过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕那英雄传说也是捏造的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于身为佣兵忍者的我们而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是财源吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我拿出真本领
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没必要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一来 看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了社会 为了人民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保卫世界和平的伟大忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己大爷就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己真帅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己如果动真格的 一定很了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能在战场上鹤立鸡群
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要做农活 我要当英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来你又是漩涡鸣人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 邦纳…不是 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有猎物了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行商人你该不会输了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无怨无仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此相遇就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我漩涡鸣人留下买路财吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是正是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实放下的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 那些家伙不是旅行商人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你会自动送上门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙才不是漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是个废物盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这家伙的外貌符合消息所述
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还带有木叶的护额
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这家伙的同伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢来捣乱的话 连你一起收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没那回…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…我是漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙才不是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深山老林里出来的农二代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿干农活 以为自己是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天想抓我出名 死缠不休
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山寨忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然连你一起收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子终于不闹腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶紧赶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们交给我的盗贼被其他的盗贼给劫走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想请你们替我夺回那个盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是忍者大师来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己动手不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那个…现在…我有点…不在状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者还要看什么状态吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我们有急事必须走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且你是官府中人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回衙门找人帮忙不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是盗贼抢走盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也就是窝里反而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙虽然是个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也并非穷凶极恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙因为外表凶悍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直被大家讨厌 欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去就一直很胆小 很善良
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善于照顾他人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当了解那家伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是官府中人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就让人觉得很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 我老实坦白所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所有的经过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥做这种蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是拯救了木叶的英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然他是同伴 为什么让他做这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然他是同伴 为什么不替他想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说…说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才不是什么同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是图个方便才不会理他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是什么同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然说不是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你而言 那家伙算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你一直把他当笨蛋耍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那家伙从小就和你在一起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一同走到现在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还不算同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有时间确实可以听听你的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们不能轻易暴露身份和所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你忘记见到过我们的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 拜托了 我一个人办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莫能助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己做决定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…是同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起爆符
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是这家伙的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是同伴 也不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是我的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个没用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不救你的话 我们的计划可就搁浅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我像个鬼一样被大家厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有伊己愿意和我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 我也被其他人欺负啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说只要我整你 就不会再欺负我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己跟我成为了挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来 漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再让你逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们看看我们最后的志气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管到哪里 我都会跟着伊己的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么点本事还想赢我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活捉漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个不用留活口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能像漩涡鸣人那样厉害就能保护伊己了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你把我当成你的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你们两个 看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时仅凭你的只言片语无法让人信服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就试探了你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试探我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在非常感动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有弃朋友于不顾 信任朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位大爷 你们以为是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位传说中的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是保护了木叶的英雄 漩涡鸣人大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给力点 你可是鸣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是天下的英雄 漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人 一生一次的大暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把漩涡鸣人的名字还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这名号我可伤不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们接下来想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为忍者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会经历如此恐怖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不太适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要回故乡去过平凡的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能和伊己一起 去哪儿都行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乐地活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挚友真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们总有一天会像他们一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂隐上忍 手鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受我的挑战吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾名为猿飞木叶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三代火影之孙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人哥哥的爱徒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.51,0:22:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.86,0:22:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不接受挑战的话
